#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Poročila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Reports View is a tabbed display. The <guilabel>Reports</guilabel> tab "
"is always displayed, and lists all available reports, grouped under the "
"headings listed and described below. You can click <quote>></quote> to "
"expand or collapse the specific reports under each heading. When you open "
"any report, it is displayed in an additional tab, labelled with the name of "
"that report."
msgstr ""
"Pogled poročil je prikaz z zavihki. Zavihek <guilabel>Poročila</guilabel> je "
"vedno prikazan in navaja vsa razpoložljiva poročila, združena pod naslovi, "
"ki so navedeni in opisani spodaj. Lahko kliknete <quote>></quote>, da "
"razširite ali strnete določena poročila pod vsakim naslovom. Ko odprete "
"katero koli poročilo, se prikaže v dodatnem zavihku, označenem z imenom tega "
"poročila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of reports is always sorted first by the group name (by number) and "
"then by report name. Clicking the <quote>Reports</quote> heading will "
"reverse the sort order. You can also click the <quote>Comment</quote> header "
"to sort by the report comment instead of name. The report's name and comment "
"can be set or edited on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab of the <link "
"linkend=\"details.reports.config\">Report Configuration</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Seznam poročil je vedno razvrščen najprej po imenu skupine (po številki) in "
"nato po imenu poročila. Če kliknete naslov <quote>Poročila</quote>, se "
"vrstni red razvrščanja obrne. Lahko tudi kliknete glavo <quote>Komentar</"
"quote>, da razvrstite komentarje poročila namesto po imenu. Ime in komentar "
"poročila lahko nastavite ali uredite na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> "
"pogovornega okna <link linkend=\"details.reports.config\">Konfiguracija "
"poročila</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Reports"
msgstr "Razpoložljiva poročila"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>reports view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled poročil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>reports view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled poročil</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Income and Expenses"
msgstr "Prihodki in odhodki"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The reports in this section show your income and expenses either for the "
"current month, for each month in the current year, or for each year. Of "
"course, the duration of the overall report and the duration captured by each "
"column can be configured to your liking. Various Graphs and Pie Charts also "
"may be produced."
msgstr ""
"Poročila v tem razdelku prikazujejo vaše prihodke in odhodke za tekoči "
"mesec, za vsak mesec v tekočem letu ali za vsako leto. Seveda lahko trajanje "
"celotnega poročila in trajanje, ki ga zajame vsak stolpec, konfigurirate po "
"svojih željah. Izdelati je mogoče tudi različne grafe in krožne diagrame."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Net Worth"
msgstr "Neto vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here there are reports that describe your net worth, either at the current "
"moment, every month for the current year, or every year of your history. In "
"addition, there is a 7-day Cash Flow Forecast and a Net Worth Graph. There "
"are also reports to get the balances for all of your accounts at any given "
"point in time."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj so poročila, ki opisujejo vašo neto vrednost, bodisi v nekem trenutku, "
"ob vsakem mesecu v tekočem letu ali za vsako leto vaše zgodovine. Poleg tega "
"sta na voljo 7-dnevna napoved denarnega toka in graf neto vrednosti. "
"Obstajajo tudi poročila za pridobitev stanja za vse vaše račune v danem "
"trenutku."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transactions"
msgstr "Transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section includes reports that list individual transactions. This is the "
"best way to print your account register for a specific period of time. The "
"transactions printed can be grouped together according to your liking by "
"choosing the appropriate report, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vključuje poročila, ki navajajo posamezne transakcije. To je "
"najboljši način za tiskanje registra vaših računov za določeno časovno "
"obdobje. Natisnjene transakcije lahko združite skupaj po svojih željah, tako "
"da izberete ustrezno poročilo, kot je:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Account"
msgstr "Po računu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Category"
msgstr "Po kategoriji"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Month or Week"
msgstr "Po mesecu ali tednu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Payee"
msgstr "Po prejemniku plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Reconciliation Status"
msgstr "Po stanju usklajevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "By Tag"
msgstr "Po znački"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cash Flow"
msgstr "Denarni tok"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Cash Flow report is similar to a Transaction report, but it displays all "
"cash-flow related transactions for the specified period, which defaults to "
"the current month."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo o denarnem toku je podobno poročilu o transakcijah, vendar "
"prikazuje vse transakcije, povezane z denarnim tokom, za določeno obdobje, "
"ki je privzeto nastavljen na trenutni mesec."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investments"
msgstr "Naložbe"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These reports help you keep track of your investments. They only include "
"investment accounts. There are a variety of presentation filters and styles, "
"as shown in this partial list."
msgstr ""
"Ta poročila vam pomagajo spremljati svoje naložbe. Vključujejo samo "
"naložbene račune. Obstajajo številni predstavitveni filtri in slogi, kot je "
"prikazano na tem delnem seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment Transactions: Similar to a Transactions report, but it includes "
"share prices and quantities."
msgstr ""
"Naložbene transakcije: Podobno poročilu o transakcijah, a vključuje cene "
"delnic in količine."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment Holdings by Account: Shows the current shares, prices, and values "
"for each account."
msgstr ""
"Naložbeni deleži po računu: prikazuje trenutne delnice, cene in vrednosti za "
"vsak račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment Holdings by Type: Same as the previous report, but organizes the "
"accounts by type (Stock, Mutual Fund, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Naložbeni deleži po vrsti: Enako kot prejšnje poročilo, vendar so računi "
"organizirani po vrsti (delnice, vzajemni skladi, &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment Performance by Account: Shows the annualized performance over any "
"period of time. This performs a cash flow analysis of all money coming into "
"and going out of the account. As a result, this is a very accurate picture "
"of how well your investments are doing."
msgstr ""
"Uspešnost naložbe po računu: prikazuje uspešnost na letni ravni v katerem "
"koli časovnem obdobju. To izvede analizo denarnega toka vsega denarja, ki "
"prihaja na račun in gre z njega. Posledično je to zelo natančna slika, kako "
"uspešne so vaše naložbe."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment Performance by Type: Same as the previous report, but organizes "
"the accounts by type (Stock, Mutual Fund, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Uspešnost naložbe po vrsti: Enako kot prejšnje poročilo, vendar so računi "
"organizirani po vrsti (delnice, vzajemni skladi, &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are also graphs for Investment Prices and Investment Worth."
msgstr "Obstajajo tudi grafi za naložbene cene in vrednost naložbe."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taxes"
msgstr "Davki"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tax reports are just like the transactions reports, with the addition "
"that only Tax related categories are included. This allows you to flag "
"certain categories as being tax-related, and then get one big report at the "
"end of the year to see the transactions for those categories all in one "
"place. They may be listed either by Category or by Payee, and for the last "
"fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"Davčna poročila so enaka kot poročila o transakcijah, z dodatkom, da so "
"vključene samo kategorije, povezane z davki. To vam omogoča, da določene "
"kategorije označite kot povezane z davki, nato pa ob koncu leta dobite eno "
"veliko poročilo, da vidite vse transakcije za te kategorije na enem mestu. "
"Lahko so navedeni po kategoriji ali po prejemniku plačila in za zadnje "
"fiskalno leto."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budgeting"
msgstr "Načrtovanje proračuna"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The budgeting reports are similar to net worth reports, but the reports can "
"display the budget for a given year, or even compare it to the actual income "
"and expenses for the same period."
msgstr ""
"Poročila o proračunu so podobna poročilom o neto vrednosti, vendar lahko "
"poročila prikažejo proračun za določeno leto ali ga celo primerjajo z "
"dejanskimi prihodki in odhodki za isto obdobje."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forecast"
msgstr "Napoved"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The forecast reports are just like the net worth reports, but they use the "
"information to display forecast information. You can display the information "
"at various levels and for the time frame of your choosing."
msgstr ""
"Poročila o napovedih so podobna poročilom o neto vrednosti, vendar "
"uporabljajo informacije za prikaz informacij o napovedih. Informacije lahko "
"prikažete na različnih ravneh in za časovni okvir po vaši izbiri."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These reports display non-transaction information about accounts, loans, and "
"schedules."
msgstr ""
"Ta poročila prikazujejo netransakcijske informacije o računih, posojilih in "
"časovnih planih."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Charts"
msgstr "Grafikoni"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <link linkend=\"details.reports.charts\">Charts</link> are enabled, this "
"section lists all the reports which are marked to display a graphical chart "
"as the default. They are also listed in one of the other sections, but they "
"are aggregated here for your easy reference."
msgstr ""
"Če so <link linkend=\"details.reports.charts\">Grafikoni</link> omogočeni, "
"so v tem razdelku navedena vsa poročila, ki so označena za privzeti grafični "
"prikaz grafikona. Navedeni so tudi v enem od drugih razdelkov, vendar so "
"tukaj združeni za lažjo uporabo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Favorite Reports"
msgstr "Priljubljena poročila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section lists all the reports you have marked as a favorite in the "
"report configuration dialog. They are still listed in one of the other "
"sections, but they are aggregated here for your easy reference. Favorite "
"reports can also be included on the Home View for even easier reference."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku so navedena vsa poročila, ki ste jih v pogovornem oknu za "
"konfiguracijo poročila označili kot priljubljena. Še vedno so navedeni v "
"enem od drugih razdelkov, vendar so tukaj združeni za lažjo uporabo. "
"Priljubljena poročila lahko vključite tudi v domači pogled za še lažjo "
"uporabo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working With Reports"
msgstr "Delo s poročili"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a number of actions you can take on each report. You can access "
"some these by right-clicking the report name in the list of reports, which "
"brings up the <guilabel>Report options</guilabel> context menu. Alternately, "
"once you have run a report, there are buttons across the top of the view to "
"invoke each of these:"
msgstr ""
"Za vsako poročilo lahko izvedete več dejanj. Do nekaterih lahko dostopate "
"tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete ime poročila na seznamu poročil, kar "
"prikliče kontekstni meni <guilabel>Možnosti poročila</guilabel>. Ko zaženete "
"poročilo, so na vrhu pogleda gumbi za priklic vsakega od teh:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Chart: Only present if the report is capable of displaying a chart. Clicking "
"this option toggles between the report and the chart."
msgstr ""
"Grafikon: prisoten samo, če poročilo lahko prikaže grafikon. S klikom na to "
"možnost preklapljate med poročilom in grafikonom."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure report: Change the properties of this report. You can customize "
"the report to your liking and save it for future use. See the next section "
"for more details"
msgstr ""
"Konfiguriraj poročilo: Spremenite lastnosti tega poročila. Poročilo lahko "
"prilagodite svojim željam in ga shranite za prihodnjo uporabo. Za več "
"podrobnosti si oglejte naslednji razdelek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New report: Create a new, customized report based on the selected report."
msgstr ""
"Novo poročilo: ustvarite novo, prilagojeno poročilo na podlagi izbranega "
"poročila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Export report: Reports can be exported, or saved, in &HTML; or CSV format. "
"&HTML; is intended to preserve the displayed formatting of the report. CSV "
"exports the data underlying the report."
msgstr ""
"Izvozi poročilo: Poročila je mogoče izvoziti ali shraniti v formatu &HTML; "
"ali CSV. &HTML; je namenjen ohranjanju prikazanega oblikovanja poročila. CSV "
"izvozi podatke, na katerih temelji poročilo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete report: Customized reports can be deleted. The default reports that "
"ship with &kmymoney; cannot be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Izbriši poročilo: Prilagojena poročila je mogoče izbrisati. Privzetih "
"poročil, ki so priložena &kmymoney; ni mogoče izbrisati."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Close report</guilabel> button was removed in 5.2. To close "
"the current report tab, click the small <guilabel>x</guilabel> to the right "
"of the report name on the tab."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guilabel>Zapri poročilo</guilabel> je bil odstranjen v 5.2. Če želite "
"zapreti trenutni zavihek poročila, kliknite majhen <guilabel>x</guilabel> "
"desno od imena poročila na zavihku."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Reports"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje poročil"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with custom reports"
msgstr "Delo s poročili po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the default reports or create your own from them by "
"selecting <guilabel>New report</guilabel>, and then configuring the new "
"report. When you click <guilabel>Configure report</guilabel> you will be "
"presented with the Report Tab of the <guilabel>Report Configuration</"
"guilabel> dialog. Initially, the new report it is named the same as the old "
"report with <quote>(Customized)</quote> added to the end. You can change the "
"name to whatever you want. You can even name your custom reports the same as "
"a default report, or the same as another custom report. You can use the "
"Comment field to further distinguish reports."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko privzeta poročila ali iz njih ustvarite svoja, tako da "
"izberete <guilabel>Novo poročilo</guilabel> in nato konfigurirate novo "
"poročilo. Ko kliknete <guilabel>Konfiguriraj poročilo</guilabel>, se vam "
"prikaže zavihek Poročilo v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Konfiguracija poročila</"
"guilabel>. Na začetku je novo poročilo poimenovano enako kot staro poročilo, "
"na koncu pa je dodan <quote>(Prilagojeno)</quote>. Ime lahko spremenite v "
"katero koli želite. Poročila po meri lahko celo poimenujete enako kot "
"privzeto poročilo ali enako kot drugo poročilo po meri. Za nadaljnje "
"razlikovanje poročil lahko uporabite polje Komentar."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Report Configuration dialog has a <guilabel>Report</guilabel> tab and a "
"<guilabel>Filters</guilabel> tab, which each have a number of subtabs. Each "
"subtab displays options for configuring different aspects of the report. "
"Note that specific subtabs and options within them may not appear if they "
"are not relevant to the report being configured."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno Konfiguracija poročila ima zavihek <guilabel>Poročilo</"
"guilabel> in zavihek <guilabel>Filtri</guilabel>, ki imata več podzavihkov. "
"Vsak podzavihek prikazuje možnosti za konfiguracijo različnih vidikov "
"poročila. Upoštevajte, da se določeni podzavihki in možnosti znotraj njih "
"morda ne bodo prikazali, če niso pomembni za poročilo, ki se konfigurira."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Report Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Poročilo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where you configure general information about the report as well as "
"controlling details about what data is presented and how it is presented."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj konfigurirate splošne informacije o poročilu ter nadzirate podrobnosti "
"o tem, kateri podatki so predstavljeni in kako so predstavljeni."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "General subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek Splošno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>report configuration report tab general subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>splošen podzavihek poročila o konfiguraciji poročila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>report configuration report tab general subtab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>splošen podzavihek poročila o konfiguraciji poročila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you set the basic properties of the report."
msgstr "Tukaj nastavite osnovne lastnosti poročila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Report Name: Choose or edit the name for this report."
msgstr "Ime poročila: izberite ali uredite ime za to poročilo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comment: Enter a comment to help you remember the details of this report and "
"identify it if the name is the same as any other report."
msgstr ""
"Komentar: Vnesite komentar, da si boste lažje zapomnili podrobnosti tega "
"poročila in ga prepoznali, če je ime tega enako kot katero koli drugo "
"poročilo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Convert values to base currency: Select this option to convert all values in "
"the report to your base currency. Leave it unchecked if you'd like to see "
"values in their original currency. If currencies are not converted, then "
"subtotals will not be shown."
msgstr ""
"Pretvori vrednosti v osnovno valuto: izberite to možnost, če želite "
"pretvoriti vse vrednosti v poročilu v svojo osnovno valuto. Pustite "
"nepotrjeno, če želite videti vrednosti v izvirni valuti. Če valute niso "
"pretvorjene, vmesne vsote ne bodo prikazane."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark as favorite report: Check this to cause this report to show up on the "
"Home View and in the group of <guilabel>Favorite Reports</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Označi kot priljubljeno poročilo: Označite to možnost, da se to poročilo "
"prikaže v domačem pogledu in v skupini <guilabel>Priljubljena poročila</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skip value if price is zero: This option is only used for investments "
"reports which show prices instead of balances as all other reports do. "
"Selecting this option includes prices only if there is an actual price for "
"the date; otherwise 0 will be shown. In a graph, the value will be skipped. "
"If this option is off, the last existing price is shown for a period. If it "
"is on, in a table <quote>0</quote> is shown, and in a chart a linear "
"interpolation for the missing values will be performed."
msgstr ""
"Preskoči vrednost, če je cena enaka nič: ta možnost se uporablja samo za "
"poročila o naložbah, ki prikazujejo cene namesto stanj, kot so vsa druga "
"poročila. Izbira te možnosti vključuje cene samo, če obstaja dejanska cena "
"za datum; drugače bo prikazana 0. V grafu bo vrednost preskočena. Če je ta "
"možnost izklopljena, je za obdobje prikazana zadnja obstoječa cena. Če je "
"vklopljen, je v tabeli prikazan <quote>0</quote>, v grafikonu pa bo izvedena "
"linearna interpolacija za manjkajoče vrednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rows/Columns subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek Vrstice/Stolpci"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where you configure how you would like the rows and columns of the "
"report to be selected and organized. This tab presents different "
"configuration options depending on the style of report you are configuring."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj konfigurirate, kako želite, da so izbrane in organizirane vrstice in "
"stolpci poročila. Ta zavihek predstavlja različne možnosti konfiguracije, "
"odvisno od sloga poročila, ki ga konfigurirate."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>report configuration report tab rows/columns subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>podzavihek poročilo o konfiguraciji vrstic/stolpcev poročila</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>report configuration report tab rows/columns subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>podzavihek poročilo o konfiguraciji vrstic/stolpcev poročila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "For income/expense and net worth reports:"
msgstr "Za poročila o prihodkih/odhodkih in neto vrednosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Budgets: If you have any <link linkend=\"details.budgets\">budgets</link> "
"defined, you can select one as well as whether differences between budget "
"and actual amounts should be propagated from one time period to the next"
msgstr ""
"Proračuni: če imate določene <link linkend=\"details.budgets\">proračune</"
"link>, lahko izberete enega in tudi, ali naj se razlike med proračunom in "
"dejanskimi zneski prenašajo iz enega časovnega obdobja v drugega"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Totals: Choose whether to display a row and/or column for total amounts."
msgstr ""
"Skupni zneski: izberite, ali želite prikazati vrstico in/ali stolpec za "
"skupne zneske."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rows: Choose whether to base the report on Income and Expense (Categories) "
"or on Asset and Liability accounts."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice: izberite, ali želite poročilo osnovati na prihodkih in odhodkih "
"(kategorije) ali na računih imetij in obveznosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detail: Choose the level of detail required for this report."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti: Izberite raven podrobnosti, ki je potrebna za to poročilo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following levels of detail are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednje ravni podrobnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "All: Show every category or account."
msgstr "Vse: Prikaži vsako kategorijo ali račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Top-Level: Show only the highest-level categories or accounts, and roll up "
"the sums of the subordinate categories or accounts into those values."
msgstr ""
"Najvišja raven: Prikažite samo kategorije ali račune na najvišji ravni in "
"združite vsote podrejenih kategorij ali računov v te vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Groups: Show only the totals of the income and expense or asset and "
"liabilities."
msgstr ""
"Skupine: Prikažite samo vsote prihodkov in odhodkov ali imetja in obveznosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Totals: Show only the grand totals."
msgstr "Seštevki vsega: Prikaži samo skupne vsote."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition you can specify whether or not to include scheduled and/or "
"transfer transactions and unused accounts or categories."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko določite, ali želite vključiti načrtovane in/ali prenosne "
"transakcije ter neuporabljene račune ali kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "For transaction reports:"
msgstr "Za poročila o transakcijah:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organize by: Choose how to group the transactions in this report."
msgstr "Organizirano po: Izberite, kako združiti transakcije v tem poročilu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show Columns: Choose which columns should be shown in the report. The date "
"and transaction amount are always shown."
msgstr ""
"Pokaži stolpce: Izberite, kateri stolpci naj bodo prikazani v poročilu. "
"Vedno sta prikazana datum in znesek transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Include only Tax Categories: Only show categories which have been marked as "
"tax-related."
msgstr ""
"Vključi samo davčne kategorije: Prikaži samo kategorije, ki so bile označene "
"kot povezane z davki."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Include only Investment Accounts: Only show transactions from investment "
"accounts."
msgstr ""
"Vključi samo naložbene račune: Prikaži samo transakcije z naložbenih računov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include only Loan Accounts: Only show transactions from loan accounts."
msgstr ""
"Vključi samo posojilne račune: Prikaži samo transakcije s posojilnih računov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Include transfers: Unless this is checked, transfer transactions are not "
"included in transaction reports"
msgstr ""
"Vključi prenose: Če to ni označeno, transakcije prenosov niso vključene v "
"poročila o transakcijah"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hide Split Transaction Details: When this option is available, it lets you "
"specify that only the total amount of a split transaction is to be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Skrij podrobnosti razdeljene transakcije: Ko je ta možnost na voljo, vam "
"omogoča, da določite, da se prikaže samo skupni znesek razdeljene "
"transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hide totals: Selecting this prevents Total lines from being calculated and "
"displayed"
msgstr ""
"Skrij vsote: če to izberete, preprečite izračun in prikaz skupnih vrstic"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Chart Subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek grafikona"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This subtab allows you to configure what the report should look like when it "
"is displayed as a chart. See the <link linkend=\"details.reports.charts"
"\">Graphs &amp; Charts</link> section for more explanation of the charting "
"functions."
msgstr ""
"Ta podzavihek vam omogoča, da konfigurirate, kako naj izgleda poročilo, ko "
"je prikazano kot grafikon. Oglejte si razdelek <link linkend=\"details."
"reports.charts\">grafe &amp; Grafikoni</link> za več razlage funkcij "
"grafikonov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>report configuration report tab chart subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>podzavihek poročila o konfiguraciji poročila grafikona</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>report configuration report tab chart subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>podzavihek poročila o konfiguraciji poročila grafikona</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Chart Type: The visual format of chart desired."
msgstr "Vrsta grafikona: Želena vizualna oblika grafikona."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show grid lines: Whether to print horizontal and vertical grid lines on the "
"chart."
msgstr ""
"Pokaži mrežne črte: Ali naj se na grafikonu natisnejo vodoravne in navpične "
"mrežne črte."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draw values on chart: Whether to print the data values on the chart itself "
"for chosen data points."
msgstr ""
"Nariši vrednosti na grafikonu: Ali naj se vrednosti podatkov natisnejo na "
"sam grafikon za izbrane podatkovne točke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show chart by default: Whether this report should first be displayed as a "
"chart when it's opened."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto pokaži grafikon: Ali naj se to poročilo, ko se odpre, najprej "
"prikaže kot grafikon."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logarithmic vertical axis: normally the vertical axis is linear."
msgstr "Logaritemska navpična os: običajno je navpična os linearna."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plot expenses downwards: normally both income and expenses are plotted "
"upwards."
msgstr ""
"Narišite odhodke navzdol: običajno so tako prihodki kot odhodki narisani "
"navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line width: The width of data lines on the chart, specified in pixels."
msgstr ""
"Širina črte: širina podatkovnih črt na grafikonu, podana v slikovnih pikah."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range Subtab"
msgstr "Podzavihek Obseg"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Range subtab has two sections, <guilabel>Date range</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Data range</guilabel> for controlling the limits and subdivisions "
"of the displayed data. Note that this only controls the display, to control "
"the data used by &kmymoney; to create the report, see the section on the "
"<link linkend=\"details.reports.config.report\">Filters tab</link>."
msgstr ""
"Podzavihek Obseg ima dva razdelka, <guilabel>Datumski obseg</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Podatkovni obseg</guilabel> za nadzor nad omejitvami in delitvami "
"prikazanih podatkov. Upoštevajte, da to nadzoruje samo prikaz za nadzor "
"podatkov, ki jih uporablja &kmymoney; Če želite ustvariti poročilo, glejte "
"razdelek na <link linkend=\"details.reports.config.report\">zavihku Filtri</"
"link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>report configuration report tab range subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>podzavihek poročila o konfiguraciji obsega poročila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>report configuration report tab range subtab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>podzavihek poročila o konfiguraciji obsega poročila</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date range"
msgstr "Datumski obseg"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting one of the descriptive values from the <guilabel>Range</guilabel> "
"dropdown automatically sets the values of the <guilabel>From</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>To</guilabel> date fields. You can override either or both of "
"those dates, in which case the first dropdown will show <quote>User defined</"
"quote>."
msgstr ""
"Izbira ene od opisnih vrednosti v spustnem meniju <guilabel>Obseg</guilabel> "
"samodejno nastavi vrednosti datumskih polj <guilabel>Od</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Do</guilabel>. Lahko preglasite enega ali oba od teh datumov, v "
"tem primeru bo prvi spustni meni pokazal <quote>Uporabniško določeno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Ticks</guilabel> dropdown controls the placement of ticks on "
"the date axis of the chart."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni <guilabel>Črtice</guilabel> nadzoruje postavitev črtic na "
"datumski osi grafikona."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data range"
msgstr "Obseg podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you control the limits, ticks, and labels on the vertical data "
"axis. The default value for the <guilabel>Range</guilabel> dropdown is "
"<quote>Automatic</quote>, lets &kmymoney; choose reasonable values for the "
"other fields. If you select <quote>User defined</quote> you need to specify "
"all the other fields. <guilabel>From</guilabel> and <guilabel>To</guilabel> "
"set the lower and upper limits of the axis. <guilabel>Major tick length</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Minor tick length</guilabel> control the positioning "
"of larger and smaller tick marks along the axis. <guilabel>Labels Precision</"
"guilabel> controls the number of decimal places used in the numbers "
"displayed along the axis."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča nadzor omejitev, črtic in oznak na navpični podatkovni osi. "
"Privzeta vrednost za spustni meni <guilabel>Obseg</guilabel> je "
"<quote>Samodejno</quote>, kar omogoča da &kmymoney; izbere razumne vrednosti "
"za druga polja. Če izberete <quote>Uporabniško določeno</quote>, morate "
"določiti vsa druga polja. <guilabel>Od</guilabel> in <guilabel>Do</guilabel> "
"nastavita spodnjo in zgornjo mejo osi. <guilabel>Dolžina glavne črtice</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Dolžina manjše črtice</guilabel> nadzorujeta položaj "
"večjih in manjših oznak vzdolž osi. <guilabel>Natančnost oznak</guilabel> "
"nadzira število decimalnih mest uporabljenih v številih prikazanih vzdolž "
"osi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filters tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Filtri"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filters tab has several subtabs, which can be used to filter or limit "
"the data &kmymoney; uses to prepare the report. These are the same subtabs "
"used to control searching for transactions. Please refer to the <link "
"linkend=\"details.search\">Search Transactions</link> section for details on "
"those tabs."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek filtri ima več podzavihkov, ki jih lahko uporabite za filtriranje "
"ali omejitev podatkov, ki jih &kmymoney; uporablja za pripravo poročila. To "
"so isti podzavihki, ki se uporabljajo za nadzor iskanja transakcij. Za "
"podrobnosti o teh zavihkih glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"details.search"
"\">Iskanje transakcij</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "Report Plugin Configuration"
msgstr "Poročilo o konfiguraciji vtičnika"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Behind the scenes, Reports are actually implemented as a plugin in "
"&kmymoney;, and there are some items which can be configured through the "
"<link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins.reports\">Reports View Plugin "
"Configuration</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"V zaledju so poročila dejansko implementirana kot vtičnik v &kmymoney; in "
"obstaja nekaj elementov, ki jih je mogoče konfigurirati v pogovornem oknu "
"<link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins.reports\">Konfiguracija vtičnika "
"pogleda poročil</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-reports.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>report plugin configuration</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>sporočilo o konfiguraciji vtičnika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-reports.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>report plugin configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>sporočilo o konfiguraciji vtičnika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum number of legend items to display</guilabel> limits the "
"number of items to list in the legend of the graph or chart display of a "
"report. This can be useful if there are enough items that the legend would "
"otherwise overwhelm the main display."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Največje število elementov legende za prikaz</guilabel> omejuje "
"število elementov za seznam v legendi prikaza grafa ali grafikona poročila. "
"To je lahko uporabno, če je dovolj elementov, da bi legenda sicer prekrila "
"glavni zaslon."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Charts line width</guilabel> is the default width in pixels of any "
"lines in the chart display of a report."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Širina črte grafikona</guilabel> je privzeta širina v slikovnih "
"pikah katere koli vrstice v prikazu grafikona v poročilu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Charts palette</guilabel> gives some choice in the array of colors "
"used in graphs and chart displays of a report."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Paleta grafikonov</guilabel> ponuja nekaj izbire v nizu barv, "
"uporabljenih v grafih in prikazih grafikonov v poročilu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since the graph and chart displays of reports are shown using HTML, the "
"<guilabel>Default CSS file</guilabel> lets you provide a css file to "
"customize these displays."
msgstr ""
"Ker so prikazi grafov in grafikonov poročil prikazani z uporabo HTML-ja, vam "
"<guilabel>Privzeta datoteka CSS</guilabel> omogoča, da zagotovite datoteko "
"css za prilagajanje teh prikazov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graphs &amp; Charts"
msgstr "Grafi &amp; Grafikoni"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing as a Chart"
msgstr "Ogled kot grafikon"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many reports can be viewed in either textual form or graphical (chart) form. "
"The same report configuration parameters are used in either case. You can "
"easily jump back and forth between the textual and graphical forms by "
"pressing the <guibutton>Chart</guibutton> or <guibutton>Report</guibutton> "
"buttons along the top of the Report View."
msgstr ""
"Številna poročila si lahko ogledate v besedilni ali grafični obliki (graf). "
"V obeh primerih so uporabljeni isti konfiguracijski parametri poročila. Med "
"besedilnimi in grafičnimi oblikami lahko enostavno skačete naprej in nazaj s "
"pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Grafikon</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Poročilo</"
"guibutton> na vrhu pogleda poročila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please pay attention to the amount of data you choose to display on a chart. "
"If you are not careful, using the same configuration for both textual and "
"graphical forms means it's possible to configure a chart to be visually "
"cluttered, unappealing, and uninformative. &kmymoney; will not force you to "
"keep your charts readable and useful! Also be aware that some reports will "
"take a long time to calculate and display if too much is included."
msgstr ""
"Bodite pozorni na količino podatkov, ki jih izberete za prikaz na grafikonu. "
"Če niste previdni, uporaba iste konfiguracije za besedilne in grafične "
"oblike pomeni, da je mogoče grafikon konfigurirati tako, da bo vizualno "
"natrpan, neprivlačen in neinformativen. &kmymoney; vas ne bo prisilil, da "
"bodo vaši grafikoni berljivi in ​​uporabni! Zavedajte se tudi, da bo izračun "
"in prikaz nekaterih poročil trajal dolgo, če je vključenega vsega preveč."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Chart Types"
msgstr "Razpoložljive vrste grafikonov"

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Graph"
msgstr "Črtni graf"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A line graph is one of the simplest forms of a chart. There is one line for "
"each series. Usually, a series is data from a single account or category "
"over time; see below for more details. The time periods stretch out along "
"the bottom axis, and the currency values are along the left axis."
msgstr ""
"Črtni graf je ena najpreprostejših oblik grafikona. Za vsako serijo je ena "
"črta. Ponavadi so nizi podatki iz enega samega računa ali kategorije skozi "
"čas; glejte spodaj za več podrobnosti. Časovna obdobja se raztezajo vzdolž "
"spodnje osi, vrednosti valut pa vzdolž leve osi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The detail level for each line is controlled in the <link linkend=\"details."
"reports.config.rowscolumns\">Rows/Columns</link> Subtab of chart "
"configuration. If you choose the <quote>Top-Level</quote> detail level, "
"there will be one line for each of the top-most accounts or categories, "
"which shows the sum total of all underlying accounts or categories. If you "
"choose <quote>Groups,</quote> it will instead show one line each for Income, "
"Expenses, Assets, or Liabilities, depending on the other settings."
msgstr ""
"Raven podrobnosti za vsako črto je nadzorovana v podzavihku <link linkend="
"\"details.reports.config.rowscolumns\">Vrstice/Stolpci</link> konfiguracije "
"grafikona. Če izberete raven podrobnosti <quote>Najvišja raven</quote>, bo "
"za vsakega od najvišjih računov ali kategorij ena črta, ki prikazuje vsoto "
"vseh osnovnih računov ali kategorij. Če izberete <quote>Skupine</quote>, bo "
"namesto tega prikazana po ena črta za prihodke, stroške, imetja ali "
"obveznosti, odvisno od drugih nastavitev."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bar Graph"
msgstr "Stolpčni graf"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bar graph works exactly the same as the line graph, except there is one "
"bar for each series in each time slice."
msgstr ""
"Stolpični graf deluje popolnoma enako kot črtni graf, le da je v vsaki "
"časovni rezini ena vrstica za vsako serijo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pie Chart"
msgstr "Krožni diagram"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pie chart is the simplest chart type available. It shows data from only "
"one time slice, as opposed to showing the values across time. This chart "
"shows only the data from the totals column of whatever report is selected. "
"If your report is configured to NOT convert values to the base currency, "
"there will be no totals column, in which case this report is not useful."
msgstr ""
"Krožni grafikon je najpreprostejša razpoložljiva vrsta grafikona. Prikazuje "
"podatke samo iz ene časovne rezine, v nasprotju s prikazovanjem vrednosti "
"skozi čas. Ta grafikon prikazuje samo podatke iz stolpca s skupnimi "
"vrednostmi katerega koli izbranega poročila. Če je vaše poročilo "
"konfigurirano tako, da NE pretvarja vrednosti v osnovno valuto, ne bo "
"stolpca s skupnimi vrednostmi, v tem primeru to poročilo ni uporabno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-reports.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ring Chart"
msgstr "Obročasti grafikon"

#. Tag: para
#: details-reports.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ring chart is very similar to a pie chart, except there is one "
"<quote>ring</quote> for each time slice in the report."
msgstr ""
"Obročasti grafikon je zelo podoben krožnemu grafikonu, le da je en "
"<quote>obroč</quote> za vsako časovno rezino v poročilu."

